
scrapy crawl rumours -o items.json

The following command will silence the log (--nolog) while at the same time sending what would normally go to the file to your STDOUT instead (-o /dev/stdout):
scrapy crawl rumours -t jsonlines --nolog -o /dev/stdout

Additionally, the following export formats are available:
'xml', 'jsonlines', 'jl', 'json', 'csv', 'pickle', 'marshal'

